About BitEX
BitEX is operated by Hong Kong BitExchange Company Limitted. Hong Kong BitExchange Company Limitted registered in 2013. BitEX is a next-generation crypto bond exchange platform designed for both beginners and experienced traders. Our mission is to provide a secure, fast, and user-friendly trading experience. Focus to improve the bond industry by changing the trading mechanism of bonds, improving the security and convenience of storage, and giving bonds the payment function of currency.
